help

No worries, I'm here to help! Here are the commands you can use:
- `!products`: Browse our full range of available products.
- `!add [Product ID]`: Place a product into your shopping cart using its ID.
- `!remove [Product ID]`: Remove an item from your cart by specifying its ID.
- `!cart`: Check the contents of your shopping cart.
- `!checkout`: Proceed to calculate the total cost of your cart, including tax.
- `!joke`: Ask me to tell you a funny joke.
- `? [Your message]`: Initiate a private chat with me for personal assistance.
